"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Curated collections</span><h2>Choose the vibe that fits your next outing</h2><p>Segmented park groupings built from live data so you can jump straight to the experiences that matter most.</p></div><div class=\"park-type-guide-wrapper\"><section id=\"park-types-guide\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d park-types-guide-section\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d collection-cards-grid\"><article class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d collection-guide-card \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-header\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-header-top\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d spots-pill\">6<!-- --> spots</span><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-rating\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-star-fill\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">4.5<!-- --> avg</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-type-info\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d type-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-tree-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\"><h3 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Dog Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d short-description\">Traditional outdoor off‑leash areas and fenced runs, optimized for everyday exercise.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-content \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What is it?</h4><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Traditional outdoor off-leash areas where dogs can run freely and socialize with other dogs.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Key Features</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d features-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Fenced enclosures</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Open grass areas</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Agility equipment</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Water stations</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Waste disposal</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Best For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">High-energy dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Owners looking for free exercise options</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash (for entering/exiting)</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Waste bags</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Toys</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Check park rules before visiting</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog&#x27;s vaccinations up to date</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Supervise your dog at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Clean up after your dog immediately</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other dogs and owners</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></button><a class=\"jump-link\" href=\"#dog-park-parks\">Jump to list<i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></a></div></article></div></section></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>6</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Columbia Cosmopolitan Recreation Area (Cosmo Park)</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.7</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Twin Lakes Dog Park</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.7</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Garth Nature Area Dog Park</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.6</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Columbia</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Columbia dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Columbia</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Columbia</h3><p>6<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.5<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">6</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/columbia-cosmopolitan-recreation-area-cosmo-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Columbia Cosmopolitan Recreation Area (Cosmo Park)</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes tomorrow at 12:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Columbia<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Columbia&#x27;s largest park, with ball fields, tennis courts, a golf course, trails &amp; fishing ponds. Contact us at (573) 874-7460. Visit our website at https://www.como.gov/parksandrec/park/columbia-cosmopolitan-recreation-area/.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 11:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Columbia<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Dog Park is a favorite spot for dog owners in Columbia.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. With a solid 4.4-star rating from over 158 reviews, it&#x27;s a highly recommended community favorite. Make sure to check the [official page](https://www.como.gov/dog-parks-leash-free-areas/) for membership info. For more dog-friendly spots, browse [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/garth-nature-area-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Garth Nature Area Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 11:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Columbia<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Garth Nature Area Dog Park is a favorite spot for dog owners in Columbia.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. With a solid 4.6-star rating from over 413 reviews, it&#x27;s a highly recommended community favorite. Make sure to check the [official page](https://www.como.gov/parksandrec/park/garth-nature-area/) for membership info. For more dog-friendly spots, browse [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/noma-north-main-bark-park-members-only\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">NOMA (North Main) Bark Park - Members only</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 11:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Columbia<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">NOMA (North Main) Bark Park - Members only provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of Columbia.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. With a solid 4-star rating from over 211 reviews, it&#x27;s a highly recommended community favorite. Plan your visit today! For rules and hours, see the [park website](http://nomabarkpark.org/) or verify details on [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/twin-lakes-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Twin Lakes Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 11:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Columbia<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Twin Lakes Dog Park provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of Columbia.\n\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. With a solid 4.7-star rating from over 563 reviews, it&#x27;s a highly recommended community favorite. For more details, you can visit the [official website](http://www.como.gov/ParksandRec/Parks_and_Facilities/dogrunningareas.php#twinlakes) or check out local guides at [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/twin-lakes-recreation-area\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Twin Lakes Recreation Area</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 11:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Columbia<!-- -->, <!-- -->MO</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Park with a large BBQ/picnic pavilion, lake for boating/fishing &amp; a seasonal, outdoor water park. Contact us at (573) 874-7111. Visit our website at http://www.como.gov/ParksandRec/Parks/Twin_Lakes/index.php.</p></div></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!