s\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJc2jdyXi23IcRBCRQ2v1oppE\",\"name\":\"Twin Lakes Dog Park\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Twin Lakes Dog Park provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of Columbia.\\n\\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional staff on-site, convenient onsite services, ensuring a comfortable visit for both you and your pet. With a solid 4.7-star rating from over 563 reviews, it's a highly recommended community favorite. For more details, you can visit the [official website](http://www.como.gov/ParksandRec/Parks_and_Facilities/dogrunningareas.php#twinlakes) or check out local guides at [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).\",\"slug\":\"twin-lakes-dog-park\",\"address\":\"2500 Chapel Hill Rd\",\"street\":\"2500 Chapel Hill Rd\",\"city\":\"Columbia\",\"state\":\"MO\",\"zipCode\":\"65203\",\"full_address\":\"2500 Chapel Hill Rd, Columbia, MO 65203, USA\",\"latitude\":38.9273887,\"longitude\":-92.38009459999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJc2jdyXi23IcRBCRQ2v1oppE\",\"phone\":\"(573) 874-7460\",\"website\":\"http://www.como.gov/ParksandRec/Parks_and_Facilities/dogrunningareas.php#twinlakes\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":563,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"6:00 AM – 11:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"